      "content": "honestly, that's the only thing that kinda makes sense to me lately. like, why am i even putting in the effort to wake up and deal with the anxiety every day if the endgame is just destruction? it feels so much more logical to just... not be a part of it. it feels like anyone who says it gets better is just lying to themselves.",
